            "title": "An Island-Wide Monitoring Program Demonstrates Decline in Reporting Rate for the Christmas Island Flying-Fox Pteropus melanotus natalis",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "John C. Z.",
                    "lastName": "Woinarski"
                },
                {
