            "title": "Metabolic and Histopathological Alterations in the Fruit-Eating Bat Artibeus lituratus Induced by the Organophosphorous Pesticide Fenthion",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Thales S.",
